diff --git a/src/twisted/newsfragments/12230.feature b/src/twisted/newsfragments/12230.feature
new file mode 100644
index 00000000000..0371d187c26
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/twisted/newsfragments/12230.feature
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+twisted.python.failure.Failure creation no longer records the place where it was created. This reduces creation time by 60% at least, thereby speeding up Deferred error handling.
\ No newline at end of file
